<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA46">
<l>malaimukaṭu mēlvaittu vācukiyaic cuṟṟit</l>
<l>talaimukaṭu tāṉorukai paṟṟi – yalaimukaṭ</l>
<l>ṭaṇṭampōy nīrteṟippa vaṉṟu kaṭalkaṭaintāṉ</l>
<l>piṇṭamāy niṉṟa pirāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who that day put Vācuki on top of the mountain [and] curled [it around],</l>
<l>seizing with one hand the top of [its] head, [and] churned the ocean so that</l>
<l>the [cosmic] egg went to the top of the waves [and] water splashed,</l>
<l>he is the lord who stood there as a clod.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
